\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1\f0\fs22\lang9 You're absolutely right \f1\emdash\par
**Static Virtual Accounts are exactly what you need** for a Clannit-style app.\par
\par
Why? Because **each Tenant, Estate, or even Unit** needs a **permanent unique bank account** where they can receive payments or fund their wallet anytime \emdash  not just one-time deposits.\par
\par
---\par
\par
## \f2\u-10179?\u-8576?\f1  \f0 How Static Virtual Accounts Fit into Your Clannit Payment System\par
\par
| User Type                       | Assigned Static Virtual Account              | Purpose                                       |\par
| ------------------------------- | -------------------------------------------- | --------------------------------------------- |\par
| \f2\u-10180?\u-8224?\f1  \f0 Tenant                       | One permanent VA (wallet funding)            | Pay levies, wallet top-up, utility, rent      |\par
| \f2\u-10180?\u-8222?\f1  \f0 Estate Management            | One VA mapped to Trust/Collection Account    | Collect all tenant payments (central account) |\par
| \f3\u-10178?\u-8706?\f1  \f0 Vendors (PHCN, Water, Waste) | Optional VA                                  | Receive payouts transparently                 |\par
| \f3\u-10179?\u-9112?\u8205?\f2\u-10179?\u-9028?\f1  \f0 App Creator               | No VA \f1\emdash  you use normal bank/Paystack Billing | Receive License Fees, Commissions             |\par
\par
---\par
\par
### \f2\u-10180?\u-8273?\f1  \f0 Why Static Virtual Accounts Are Perfect:\par
\par
| Feature                    | What it means for your app                                          |\par
| -------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------- |\par
| Permanent (no expiry)      | Tenants can save the account and keep paying always                 |\par
| Unique per tenant          | Easily identify **who paid, what unit, what purpose**               |\par
| Bulk generation            | When onboarding an estate, you can auto-create 50\f1\endash 500 VAs for homes |\par
| Can be connected to wallet | Every time they transfer to VA \f4\u8594?\f1  \f0 money appears in wallet            |\par
| Can be linked to ledger    | All transactions are automatically recorded in your system          |\par
\par
