\par
### \f3\u-10178?\u-8706?\f1  \f0 Step 4: Connect to Invoice System (Bills & Levies)\par
\par
\f5\u10004?\f1  \f0 Estate Admin uploads bills (e.g., \f1\u8358?20,000 service charge)\par
\f5\u10004?\f1  \f0 Tenant pays using their VA \f4\u8594?\f1  \f0 Wallet credited \f4\u8594?\f1  \f0 Bill auto-cleared\par
\par
\f2\u-10179?\u-8903?\f1  \f0 The ledger tracks the bill and marks it **PAID**\par
\f2\u-10179?\u-8903?\f1  \f0 Admin can see dashboard like:\par
\par
| Unit     | Bill    | Payment Date | Status  |\par
| -------- | ------- | ------------ | ------- |\par
| Block A1 | \f1\u8358?18,000 | 04/08/2025   | PAID    |\par
| Block A2 | \u8358?18,000 | 07/08/2025   | Pending |\par
| Block B1 | \u8358?18,000 | 04/08/2025   | PAID    |\par
\par
